      • LoadSheddingUnit

        public LoadSheddingUnit(String raw)
        Takes in raw data of a load shedding entry, such as "8_14_00" This method separates the stage, the day, and the hour by the '_'s separating them, and turns them into a unique integer key to be used for the binary tree.
        Parameters:
        raw - a string containing the raw data of the load shedding unit, from the given text file
